Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.87,0:00:05.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（銃声）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:08.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（藍原(あいはら)延珠(えんじゅ)）ああ… 蓮太郎(れんたろう)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:08.58,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.87,0:00:11.26,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,We're going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:11.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（里見(さとみ)蓮太郎）俺たちも行くぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:12.79,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,I will stay behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:13.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（千寿(せんじゅ)夏世(かよ)）私は残ります
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:17.73,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,If someone doesn't hold them back here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:17.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで 誰かが食い止めないと―
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:20.23,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,win or lose, we'll all die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:20.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝っても負けても全滅しますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:25.46,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Don't worry. If I'm at a disadvantage, I will run.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.73,0:00:23.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心してください
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.35,0:00:25.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,劣勢になったら 逃げますので
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:27.83,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Please take care of Shogen-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:28.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,将監(しょうげん)さんをお願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.19,0:00:29.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:30.39,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,All right. Let's go, Enju.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:31.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行くぞ 延珠！\N（延珠）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:31.17,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:46.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.74,0:02:09.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.19,0:02:13.10,Bullet_Ep_Title,title,0,0,0,,{\fad(420,420)}#04 Black Bullet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:15.40,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,It's so quiet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:15.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,静かだな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:16.29,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:16.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:19.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）うわっ… ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:20.78,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:20.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ？ これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:23.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひぃっ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:29.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（物音）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:32.57,Bullet_Main,shogen,0,0,0,,Sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:35.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伊熊(いくま)将監）剣は… 俺の剣は…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:35.13,Bullet_Main,shogen,0,0,0,,My sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:38.27,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Ikuma Shogen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:38.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伊熊… 将監か
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.96,0:02:41.54,Bullet_Main,shogen,0,0,0,,Have you... seen my sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:41.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（将監）俺の剣を知らねえか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:44.64,Bullet_Main,shogen,0,0,0,,As long as... I have that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:44.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれが あれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:47.77,Bullet_Main,shogen,0,0,0,,I can... still... fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:47.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ… 戦え…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.37,0:02:49.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,る… ううっ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.25,0:02:51.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:54.27,Bullet_Main,kohina,0,0,0,,Papa, I'm surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:54.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蛭子(ひるこ)小比奈(こひな)）パパ ビックリ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.54,0:02:55.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（２人）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:57.82,Bullet_Main,kohina,0,0,0,,He really is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:57.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小比奈）ホントに生きてたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:03.26,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,The end is near.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:03.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蛭子影胤(かげたね)）幕が近い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:06.82,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Let us finish this, Satomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:07.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決着をつけよう 里見くん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:09.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（防衛大臣）付近の民警は―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:10.99,Bullet_Main,guy,0,0,0,,With the civil officers we have \Nin the vicinity, it'd take even
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:12.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一番近くにいるペアでも\N１時間以上かかります
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:12.81,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,the closest pair at least an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:13.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ドアが開く音）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.94,0:03:15.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（聖天子(せいてんし)）あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:19.97,Bullet_Main,gramps,0,0,0,,Kisara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:19.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（天童菊之丞(てんどうきくのじょう)）木更(きさら)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:22.22,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,I called for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:22.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私(わたくし)がお呼びしました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:25.54,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,President Tendo, what would you say is the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:24.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天童社長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:27.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見ペアの勝率は\Nいかほどと見ますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:27.17,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,success rate for the Satomi pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:30.23,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,If I may voice my own expectation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:30.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（天童木更）\N私の期待を加味してよいなら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:31.72,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,they will win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ちます 絶対に！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:32.58,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:36.47,Bullet_Main,guy,0,0,0,,What? They're up against the survivor \Nof the New Humanity Creation Plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（自衛官）はあ!?\N相手は 新人類創造計画の
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:37.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き残りなんだぞ\N勝ち目なんか…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:37.56,Bullet_Main,guy,0,0,0,,They don't stand a...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:38.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.61,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Ten years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:43.63,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Gastrea came into my house \Nand devoured my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の家に ガストレアが侵入して
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,父と母を食い殺しました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:45.87,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Because of the stress I endured at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:45.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は そのときのストレスで―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:48.67,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,my kidneys are barely functioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:48.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腎臓の機能が ほぼ停止しています
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:53.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのとき 里見蓮太郎は\N私をかばって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:53.04,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,At that time, Satomi Rentaro protected me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:57.88,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,and the Gastrea took his right hand, \Nright leg, and left eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:55.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,右手 右足 左目を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:57.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガストレアに奪われました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:01.72,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,On the verge of death, \Nhe was taken to Section 22.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:01.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひん死の彼が運び込まれたのは\Nセクション22
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:04.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,執刀医は 室戸(むろと) 菫(すみれ)医師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:04.64,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,The performing surgeon was Dr. Muroto Sumire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:06.50,Bullet_Main,guy,0,0,0,,Muroto Sumire?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:06.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,室戸 菫…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:08.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ ま… まさか！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:08.81,Bullet_Main,guy,0,0,0,,I-It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.81,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,You will not retrieve the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）\N君は ケースを取り戻せない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.23,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:18.19,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,We stand in your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:18.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私たちが\N立ちはだかっているからだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:22.87,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,A second defeat, \Nthe annihilation of my comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２度の敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,味方の全滅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:26.70,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Sure! I couldn't have asked for \Na better situation, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.92,0:04:24.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:26.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,願ってもない状況だ クソ野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:28.70,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I will eliminate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様を排除する！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:30.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）フフッ…\N（指を鳴らす音）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:34.27,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Tendo Martial Arts First Style, Number 3:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:33.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天童式戦闘術 一の型三番！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:35.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,轆轤鹿伏鬼(ろくろかぶと)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.21,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Rokuro Kabuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:38.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）ハハハハ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:41.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）くっ うう…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:42.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:45.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）うおおー！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:49.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）うわっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:53.49,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,He broke through Maximum Pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.95,0:04:54.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マキシマムペインを破った!?\Nあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:05.34,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Artificial limbs made from Varanium?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:05.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バラニウムの義肢だと!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.98,0:05:07.45,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Could it be that you're also...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:07.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか 君も!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:09.85,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I'll introduce myself, as well, Kagetane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:10.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）俺も名乗るぞ 影胤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:13.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,元陸上自衛隊東部方面隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.23,0:05:13.08,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I am formerly from the Ground \NSelf-Defense Force's Eastern Force,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:17.46,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,787th Mechanization Special Unit, \Nof the New Humanity Creation Plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:15.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,７８７機械化特殊部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:17.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,新人類創造計画
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:19.46,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Satomi Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:19.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見蓮太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.40,Bullet_Main,guy,0,0,0,,There was another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:21.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（自衛官）もう１人いたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:24.21,Bullet_Main,guy,0,0,0,,Another of the human weapons \Nborn of the Gastrea War?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:24.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガストレア戦争が生んだ\N人間兵器が…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:26.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）クッ… フフッ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:28.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハハ… うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は痛い
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.04,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,I am in pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:33.47,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,I am alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は生きてる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:36.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すばらしきかな人生！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:36.02,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,What a magnificent life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.85,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Hallelujah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:37.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハレルヤ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:41.27,Bullet_Main,kohina,0,0,0,,Don't be mean to Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パパをいじめるなー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:46.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）うおー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:48.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）フフフフ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:52.17,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Cry, Sodomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:54.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,哭(な)け ソドミー\N唄え ゴスペル
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:54.24,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Sing, Gospel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:01.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:05.05,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,We were created to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:04.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）\N我々は 殺すために作られた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.54,0:06:08.03,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,If the Gastrea War were to recommence,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:07.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガストレア戦争が再開すれば―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:10.98,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,the significance of our lives will be proven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:11.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々の存在意義が証明される
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:14.70,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Are you trying to tell me... \Nthat's the reason you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:14.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）まさか 貴様\Nそのためだけに！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.61,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,What did the people around you think
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:16.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）君のイニシエーターが―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:21.03,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,when they found out your Initiator \Nwas one of the Cursed Children?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:18.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,呪われた子供たちだと\N露見したときの―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:21.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,周りの反応は どうだった？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:23.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,祝福されたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:23.17,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Did they offer their blessings?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:26.48,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Were you touched by endless cheers of joy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:26.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鳴りやまぬ歓声に\N心を洗われたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:30.56,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,The world that we wish for \Nis different from theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:30.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼らと我々が望む世界は\N違うのだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:33.59,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,We have been chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:34.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々は選ばれた者だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:37.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ 里見蓮太郎\N私と共に来い！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:36.21,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Now, Satomi Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:38.00,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:41.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ざけんじゃねえよ クソ野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:41.21,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me, you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:43.23,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,There's no way in hell
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:43.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様の語る未来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.23,0:06:45.00,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I can accept the future you're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:44.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,断じて 許容できねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:46.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）とりゃー！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.69,0:06:48.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわっ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:51.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）フハハ…\N（蓮太郎）延珠！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:51.65,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Enju!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:53.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:57.92,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,If you cannot abide...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:57.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）従えないのなら―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:06:59.31,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Then die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:06:59.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ねー！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:03.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:04.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）うっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:06.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ぐっ…\N（延珠）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:10.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:13.53,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,You have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:13.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）君の 負けだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:18.04,Bullet_Italics,ren,0,0,0,,Am I... going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:16.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）俺は―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:17.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死ぬのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:23.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ… 延珠…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:23.05,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:28.05,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro! Please do not leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:27.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎！\N妾(わらわ)を１人にしないでくれー！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:32.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ くぅ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:37.06,Bullet_Flashback,sumire,0,0,0,,The AGV experimental drug was \Ncreated from the Gastrea virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:34.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（室戸 菫）ＡＧＶ試験薬は―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガストレアウイルスによって\N生成された
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:41.31,Bullet_Flashback,sumire,0,0,0,,It gives humans the regenerative \Nabilities of the Gastrea,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:41.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガストレア並みの再生能力を\N人間に与えるが―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:45.94,Bullet_Flashback,sumire,0,0,0,,but there is a 20% chance that they \Nwill turn into Gastrea themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:45.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,20％もの確率で\Nガストレア化させてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:48.53,Bullet_Flashback,sumire,0,0,0,,If you can avoid it, don't use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:48.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できれば 使うなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:51.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ううっ うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:54.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:58.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ ぐっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.39,0:08:01.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ うっ… うわー！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:04.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎のうめき声）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:07.23,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,R-Rentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:07.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,れ… 蓮太郎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:09.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:15.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:16.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:21.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:24.13,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I won... that gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:24.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,賭けに勝ったぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:28.52,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:28.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）里見くん 君は…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:35.03,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Tendo Martial Arts Suiten Ippeki Stance:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.17,0:08:34.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,天童式戦闘術 水天一碧(すいてんいっぺき)の構え
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:37.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（小比奈）うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:39.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:41.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,雲嶺毘湖鯉鮒(うねびこりゅう)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:41.41,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Unebiko Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:47.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）あっ ああっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:52.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ ああっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:55.35,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Inzen Kokutei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:54.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隠禅(いんぜん)･哭汀(こくてい)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:58.39,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,Am I... going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:58.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（影胤）私は… 君に…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:01.27,Bullet_Main,kage,0,0,0,,lose to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:01.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けるのか…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:08.98,Bullet_Main,kohina,0,0,0,,Papa... Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:07.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パパ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:08.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パパ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:21.37,Bullet_Main,ops,0,0,0,,Hiruko Kagetane's signal has disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:21.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（オペレーター）\N蛭子影胤の反応 消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:24.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一同の歓声）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:25.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（聖天子）フゥ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:29.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（警告音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（警告音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:31.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（警告音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:32.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（警告音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:32.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:33.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:33.51,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.13,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう 大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:39.13,Bullet_Main,kohina,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:38.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パパー！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:42.16,Bullet_Main,kohina,0,0,0,,No... No, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:40.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イヤよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:42.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,イヤよ パパー！ ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:44.50,Bullet_Main,kohina,0,0,0,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:44.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パパ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（泣き声）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:49.96,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,She's no longer an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:49.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女はもう 敵じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:50.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（携帯電話の着信音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（携帯電話の着信音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ん？\N（延珠）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（携帯電話の着信音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:55.86,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I won like I promised, Kisara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:55.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,約束どおり勝ったぜ 木更さん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:58.40,Bullet_Italics,kisa,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:58.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）うん 見たわ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:00.00,Bullet_Italics,kisa,0,0,0,,But, Satomi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:09:59.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でもね 里見くん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:02.16,Bullet_Italics,kisa,0,0,0,,I've got some bad news I have to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:02.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いニュースを\N伝えなきゃならない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:06.37,Bullet_Italics,kisa,0,0,0,,A Stage Five Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:06.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ステージⅤのガストレアが―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:08.26,Bullet_Italics,kisa,0,0,0,,has shown itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:08.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,姿を現したの！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.65,0:10:17.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（スコーピオンの雄たけび）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:27.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄たけび）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:46.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄たけび）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.67,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Is everything over?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:49.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全部… 終わりなのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:52.15,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0,0,0,,We won't let it end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）まだ 終わらせない！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:55.17,Bullet_Italics,,0,0,0,,Seitenshi-sama has given her consent to my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:55.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の作戦 聖天子様から\Nお許しを頂いたわ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:58.68,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0,0,0,,The answer is to the southeast of your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:58.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,答えは 君から見て\N南東方向にある
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:02.93,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Heaven's Ladder?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:02.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）天(あま)の梯子(はしご)…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:05.56,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0,0,0,,You're going to do it, Satomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:05.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）君がやるのよ 里見くん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:09.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠･蓮太郎）ハァ ハァ ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:13.12,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,The Linear Electromagnetic Projectile Device.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:13.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）線形超電磁投射装置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:15.23,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Also known as Heaven's Ladder.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:15.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,またの名を 天の梯子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:23.68,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,A railgun module that fires metallic projectiles
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:23.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,直径800ミリ以下の\N金属飛翔体を―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:27.02,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,with a diameter less than \N800 millimeters at near light speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:27.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,亜光速まで加速して撃ち出す\Nレールガンモジュール
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:32.41,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,If we shoot Varanium rounds at a speed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:34.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,回避不可能なスピードで\Nバラニウムの弾丸を撃ち込めば―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:34.57,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,that would make regeneration impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:39.26,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,we'd be able to exterminate \Neven a Stage Five Gastrea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:39.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ステージⅤガストレアだろうと\N必ず消滅させることができるわ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:46.01,Bullet_Announcer,voice,0,0,0,,Commencing operation of the \NLinear Electromagnetic Projectile Device.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:45.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（合成音声）\N線形超電磁投射装置の\N起動を開始します
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:48.62,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Power supply, nominal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:48.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,電力供給 異常なし
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:51.89,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Dewar vessels for liquid \Nhelium storage, also nominal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:51.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,液体ヘリウム保存用の\Nデュワー瓶も異常なし
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:53.80,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Thank you, Satomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう 里見くん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:55.54,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,We'll take care of the launch sequence here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:57.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,起動後の発射シークエンスは\N全て こちらで行うわ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.15,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,as soon as everything is operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:59.93,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,So all we have to do now is watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:11:59.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは 見ているだけでいいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:02.15,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,We couldn't do anything, \Neven if they told us to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やれって言われても できねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:40.74,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,That's a Stage Five?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:40.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれが ステージⅤなのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:44.84,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Yeah. The Zodiac Gastrea: Scorpion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:41.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:45.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゾディアックガストレア･\Nスコーピオン
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:48.45,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,It's the Gastrea that almost \Ndestroyed the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:48.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かつて 世界を破滅寸前に\N追い込んだ ガストレアだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:50.50,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,We've got trouble, Satomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:50.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まずいわ 里見くん！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:52.87,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,It's displaying a message saying \Nthere's a problem in the chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:52.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チャンバー部に\N異常を伝える表示が出てる！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.24,0:12:54.59,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:54.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どういうことだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:59.31,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0,0,0,,It's possible the Varanium \Nrounds haven't been loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:57.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）もしかしたら\Nバラニウム徹甲弾が―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:59.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,装填されてないかもしれない！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:00.50,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:00.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだって!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:05.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（警告音）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:09.76,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Damn it! There aren't any rounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:09.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ 弾がない！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:13.16,Bullet_Announcer,voice,0,0,0,,Electrical power preservation system \Ncoolant leak confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.87,0:13:13.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（合成音声）電力貯蔵システム\N冷却流出を確認
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:15.39,Bullet_Announcer,voice,0,0,0,,Please halt the experiment at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:14.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,速やかに 実験を停止してください
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:15.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,速やかに 実験を停止してください
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:15.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）\Nどうする 蓮太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:15.39,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,What do we do, Rentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:18.01,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0,0,0,,Because of the magnetic field...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:18.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）磁場の影響で―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:21.41,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun, it's not responding \Nto remote commands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:21.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見くん…\N遠隔入力を受けつけないの！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.04,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:23.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見くん！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:29.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ううっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:33.79,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro, you aren't going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:33.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎 まさか お主…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:36.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ ううっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:37.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うおお…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:40.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:43.09,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I'm going to use my right arm as a shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.11,0:13:43.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の右手を弾丸に使う
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:47.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,超バラニウムなら\N問題ないはずだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:47.76,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,There shouldn't be an issue \Nif it's super Varanium.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:51.76,Bullet_Announcer,voice,0,0,0,,Varanium charge detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:51.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（合成音声）\Nバラニウム 装填を確認
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:54.06,Bullet_Main,ops,0,0,0,,We can't regain control \Nof the launch sequence!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,射撃管制 復帰できません！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:57.76,Bullet_Main,ops,0,0,0,,Without doing it manually on-site, \Nlaunch is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:57.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,管制室からの手動射撃以外\N不可能です！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:13:59.23,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun, did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見くん 聞こえた？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:02.00,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0,0,0,,We can't fire the railgun from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:02.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらから\Nレールガンは撃てないの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.73,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0,0,0,,Please! You have to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:03.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願い 君がやって！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:07.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… ちょっと 冗談だろ！\N木更さん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:07.30,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Hey, you've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.30,0:14:08.72,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,There's no way I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:09.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺には無理だって！ 木更さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:09.67,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Kisara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:12.34,Bullet_Italics,kisara,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun, the world— Please—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:11.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）里見くん\N世界を… お願い…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.97,0:14:13.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（無線が切れる音）\Nあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:15.00,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Kisara-san! Kisara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:14.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,木更さん… 木更さん！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:18.21,Bullet_Announcer,voice,0,0,0,,Energy levels at 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:18.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（合成音声）\Nエネルギー充填 100％
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.50,Bullet_Announcer,voice,0,0,0,,Initiating manual trigger system.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:20.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手動トリガーシステムを\N起動します
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:23.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:25.51,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:25.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:43.57,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,So I have to manually hit a \Ntarget 50 kilometers away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.08,0:14:41.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,距離50キロの目標に
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:43.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手動で当てんのか…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:45.57,Bullet_Main,kisara,0,0,0,,Satomi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:45.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見くん…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:47.57,Bullet_Main,seiten,0,0,0,,Satomi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:47.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見さん…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:55.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（雄たけび）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:05.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:08.63,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I can't. I can't do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:07.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダメだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:10.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やれない… 俺には…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:10.38,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:14.14,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro, I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:14.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蓮太郎 妾がいる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:17.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は… 外したら 俺たちは終わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:17.84,Bullet_Main,rentaro,0,0,0,,If we miss, we're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:19.37,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Of course we'll hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:19.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）当たるに決まってる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:24.27,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,The shell could veer toward the Tokyo Area \Nand cause an unprecedented disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:21.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,弾丸が東京エリアにそれて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:24.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,未曽有の大災厄を\Nもたらすかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:28.03,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,But if it's you, Rentaro, \Nit'll hit the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:28.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 蓮太郎なら当てる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:30.28,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:30.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延珠…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:38.35,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:38.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）\N蓮太郎だけが 世界を救える
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:42.21,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,No one else but you, Rentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:42.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほかの誰でもない 蓮太郎だけが…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.07,0:15:55.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（深呼吸）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:57.08,Bullet_Main,rentaro,0,0,0,,Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:59.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延珠 お前を絶対\N失いたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:59.22,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose you, no matter what...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:02.65,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,May I interpret that as a proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:02.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今のは プロポーズ的な\N解釈でいいのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:03.95,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:05.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アホか 家族的な解釈をしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:05.79,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Take it as me saying you're family!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:08.28,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,A ten-year-old shouldn't be talking about love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.88,0:16:08.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10歳のガキが\N愛を語るんじゃねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:10.44,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,You're not scared anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.75,0:16:10.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう 怖くはないな？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:11.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）フッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:15.70,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Yeah... Let's finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:15.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 終わりにするぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.27,0:16:31.16,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:32.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）延珠…\N（延珠）ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:32.47,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:34.97,Bullet_Main,both,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:34.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（２人）いけー！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）うっ くっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:53.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（スコーピオンの悲鳴）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:27.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:49.43,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Why didn't you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:49.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして 逃げなかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:52.88,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,So you've... found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:52.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夏世）見つかっちゃいました…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:56.56,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You said you'd run if you \Nwere at a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:57.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）\N劣勢になったら逃げるって\N言ってたじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:18:00.39,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Satomi-san, how's Shogen-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:18:00.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見さん 将監さんは？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:03.89,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,He's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:03.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無事だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:11.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:15.21,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Satomi-san... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:15.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夏世）里見さん 私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:17.85,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Yeah... There's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:20.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）ああ 間違いなく\N侵食率が50％を超えている
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:20.53,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,The corrosion rate in your body is over 50%.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.97,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Please let me die as a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:25.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人のまま 私も死なせてください
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:29.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の存在を肯定してくれた\Nあなたを―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:31.02,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,As the one who acknowledged my existence, \NI didn't want to let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.27,0:18:31.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死なせたくなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:32.99,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,So I tried hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:33.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから 頑張った
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:35.30,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,It was hard, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つらかったけど―
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:38.62,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,I'm glad I lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:39.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 生きててよかった…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:42.33,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Right now, my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.82,0:18:42.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の胸は 今…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.59,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,is filled with gratitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:44.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感謝でいっぱいです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:46.51,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:47.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:19:01.81,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Hey, Satomi-san, you don't have \Nvery many friends, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:01.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 里見さんって\Nあんまり友達いないでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:02.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:05.20,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,I'll be your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:05.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が友達になってあげます
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:08.46,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:10.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ… ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:10.13,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:13.85,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You are my irreplaceable friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:14.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は 俺の\Nかけがえのない友達だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:18.97,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Satomi-san, from here on out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:17.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（夏世）里見さん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:21.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これから先 暗闇で迷ったら―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:20.63,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,If you get lost in the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:23.77,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,follow the compass within your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:24.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心の中のコンパスに従って
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:26.14,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,and go towards the light...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:26.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,光の方に…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.01,0:19:28.47,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,Please save
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:28.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この世界を…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:30.65,Bullet_Main,natsu,0,0,0,,this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:31.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,救って…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）うう…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:35.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（銃声）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:46.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ヘリのローター音）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:20:00.32,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,About the information leaked to Kagetane...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:20:00.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）\N影胤に情報がリークされた件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:04.25,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,They're saying it was caused by Defense \NMinister Kutsuoda's party going on a rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:04.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,響田(くつわだ)防衛大臣一派の\N暴走ってことになってる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:08.52,Bullet_Main,kiku,0,0,0,,Kutsuoda just hanged himself in \Nhis detainment cell and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:08.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（菊之丞）響田は さっき\N留置場で首をつって死んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:10.89,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,He worked for you, didn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:10.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの人は あんたの部下だろうが！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:14.87,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,The New Gastrea Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:14.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガストレア新法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:19.56,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,A law that will raise the social \Nstatus of the Cursed Children...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:17.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,呪われた子供たちの\N社会的地位を―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:19.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,向上させようとする法案
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:22.91,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,But you're all for discrimination.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:23.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが あんたは\N筋金入りの差別主義者だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:25.18,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You made it known that his daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:27.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツの娘 小比奈が\Nこのテロにかんでることを公表し
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:27.41,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,Kohina, was involved in this act of terrorism,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:30.66,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,and encouraged animosity \Ntoward the Cursed Children.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:30.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,呪われた子供たちに\N反感を抱かせようとした
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:33.55,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You even tried to summon a Stage Five Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:33.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガストレア新法を止めるために―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:35.78,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,that would destroy the Tokyo Area,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:35.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,東京エリアの大絶滅を呼ぶ―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:39.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ステージⅤの召喚さえ\N実行させようとした！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:38.83,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,in order to stop the New Gastrea Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:42.23,Bullet_Main,kiku,0,0,0,,How could you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:42.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（菊之丞）なぜ 忘れられる…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:47.51,Bullet_Main,kiku,0,0,0,,Ten years ago, those bugs killed \Nmy wife and many others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:47.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10年前 我が妻が\N全ての人々が殺された日々を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:53.63,Bullet_Main,kiku,0,0,0,,They also took your arm and leg, \Nand you want me to grant the children
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:50.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の手足と両親を奪った―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:53.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの虫けらの血を宿した\Nガキどもに―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:55.81,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,who carry their blood human rights?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:56.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人権を与える？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:21:01.44,Bullet_Main,kiku,0,0,0,,They are the demons who will \Nbring destruction to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:58.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤツらこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:21:01.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この世 全てを破滅させる悪魔だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:03.87,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Those girls are human...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:04.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女たちは人間だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:07.45,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,I, Satomi Rentaro,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:07.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は… 里見蓮太郎は…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:09.82,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,believe in Aihara Enju.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:10.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,藍原延珠を信じる！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:13.23,Bullet_Main,kiku,0,0,0,,You fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:13.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（菊之丞）貴様というヤツは…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:16.33,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,You saved my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:16.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）\Nあんたは 俺の命を救ってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:19.49,Bullet_Flashback,kiku,0,0,0,,If you do not want to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:19.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死にたくなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.22,0:21:23.01,Bullet_Flashback,kiku,0,0,0,,survive, Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:23.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きろ 蓮太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:26.59,Bullet_Main,rentaro,0,0,0,,When I was in the pit of despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:26.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶望に両目を閉じたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:29.39,Bullet_Main,,0,0,0,,I would remember those \Nwords and pull through.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:29.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの言葉を思い出して\N乗り切った
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:34.62,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,I have never forgotten what \Nhappened that day ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:32.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,10年前の あの日のこと―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:35.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１日たりとも 忘れたことはない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:43.82,Bullet_Flashback,ren,0,0,0,,Seitenshi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:43.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）聖天子様―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:46.23,Bullet_Flashback,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:46.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１つ お聞きしたいことが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:47.30,Bullet_Flashback,senten,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:47.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（聖天子）なんでしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:50.58,Bullet_Flashback,ren,0,0,0,,I saw what was inside the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:50.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は ケースの中身を見た
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:51.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:56.62,Bullet_Flashback,ren,0,0,0,,A broken-down tricycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:56.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）壊れた三輪車
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:22:00.38,Bullet_Flashback,ren,0,0,0,,How the hell is that a catalyst \Nto summon a Scorpion?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:58.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ あれが\Nスコーピオンを呼び出す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.94,0:22:00.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,触媒になりえたんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:03.25,Bullet_Flashback,ren,0,0,0,,What are Gastrea, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:03.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そもそも ガストレアって\Nなんなんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.25,0:22:05.51,Bullet_Flashback,ren,0,0,0,,Please tell me, Seitenshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.36,0:22:05.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,教えてくれ 聖天子様！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:09.81,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0,0,0,,I cannot tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:07.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:10.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お教えできません
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.57,0:22:15.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.17,0:22:22.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… 蓮太郎ー！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.52,0:22:22.23,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.52,0:22:26.67,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Oh, is your arm all better?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.59,0:22:26.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おお～ 手が治ったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:27.70,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,For the most part.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.84,0:22:27.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）一応な
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:32.10,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Did Sumire tell you the results \Nof my corrosion exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.22,0:22:30.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,菫から 妾の\N侵食率検査の結果は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.89,0:22:31.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:32.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.10,0:22:34.75,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Yeah. 24.9%.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.97,0:22:34.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,24,9％だ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.03,0:22:38.99,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Oh, so it's barely changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.10,0:22:36.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.60,0:22:39.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほとんど\N変わってないのだな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.37,0:22:42.42,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0,0,0,,Satomi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.48,0:22:42.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（聖天子）里見さん…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.78,0:22:44.55,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0,0,0,,If the hierarchy were to improve,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:44.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,序列が向上すれば―
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:47.42,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0,0,0,,civil officer pairs would \Nbe given special rights:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.69,0:22:47.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,民警のペアには\N特権が与えられます
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.81,0:22:49.72,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0,0,0,,A quasi-class elevation,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.86,0:22:49.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,擬似階級の向上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.72,0:22:53.01,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0,0,0,,and the access key to top secret information.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.99,0:22:52.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 機密情報へのアクセスキー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.55,0:22:58.51,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0,0,0,,Satomi-san, rise through the ranks with Enju-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.74,0:22:55.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里見さん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:22:57.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,延珠さんと\N序列の階級を―
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.08,0:22:58.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,駆け上がるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:05.23,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0,0,0,,Then you will know
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:05.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのとき\Nあなたは知るでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.58,0:23:11.05,Bullet_Flashback,seiten,0,0,0,,the reason you were born \Nand who you truly are...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:08.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分が何者で―
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.42,0:23:11.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をなすために\N生まれてきたのかを…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.43,0:23:23.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:25.63,Corrosion_23:23,sign,0,0,0,,Corrosion Rate \N\N{\b1}42.1%
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.46,0:23:25.92,Aihara_23:23,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,390)}Aihara Enju \N\N{\b0}((Medical Chart))
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.63,0:23:28.46,Corrosion_23:23,sign,0,0,0,,Percentage Until Bodily Breakdown \N\N {\b1}7.2% Remaining
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:40.48,Bullet_Next_Ep_Title,sign,0,0,0,,#05 The Crimson Black Assassin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:32.05,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,We've got a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.53,0:23:33.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）依頼がきてるの\N内容は護衛任務
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:33.50,Bullet_Main,kisa,0,0,0,,It's a bodyguard request.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:34.80,Bullet_Main,enju,0,0,0,,Rentaro, I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:34.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（木更）依頼がきてるの\N内容は護衛任務
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:34.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）蓮太郎\Nイヤな感じがする
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:35.97,Bullet_Main,ren,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.45,0:23:34.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）蓮太郎\Nイヤな感じがする
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.62,0:23:35.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（延珠）蓮太郎\Nイヤな感じがする
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.62,0:23:35.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）てめえは 誰だ\N（マスター）お前の任務は何か
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.23,0:23:36.38,Bullet_Main,voice,0,0,0,,What is your mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.91,0:23:36.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蓮太郎）てめえは 誰だ\N（マスター）お前の任務は何か
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.38,0:23:40.06,Bullet_Main,person,0,0,0,,The assassination of the Tokyo \NArea representative, Seitenshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.91,0:23:40.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ティナ）東京エリアの代表\N聖天子の抹殺です
